Copy link to bookmark or share with others

List of Android Pie Mobile Phones List (Jul 2023) with price ranging from Rs. 4,090 to Rs. 71,990. We have found 636 phones. Here is the summary of the results:


Most popular phones: In the last 30 days, users viewed Samsung Galaxy S10 Plus, Samsung Galaxy S10 and Samsung Galaxy Note 10 Plus (Galaxy Note 10 Pro) the most.


Best phones: The best phones to buy are Samsung Galaxy S10 Plus with a spec score of 92, Samsung Galaxy S10 with a spec score of 92 and Samsung Galaxy S10 512GB with a spec score of 92.


Performance: Phones such as LG G8X ThinQ, OnePlus 7 256GB and OnePlus 7 promise smooth and lag-free performance.


Display: Smartphones like Samsung Galaxy S10, Samsung Galaxy S10 512GB and Samsung Galaxy S10 Plus have good resolution and colour reproduction.


Camera: For good image quality, phones such as Samsung Galaxy Note 10, Samsung Galaxy Note 10 Plus (Galaxy Note 10 Pro) and Samsung Galaxy S10e are good buys.


Battery: Mobiles such as Samsung Galaxy M30s 128GB, Xiaomi Redmi 8A Dual 3GB RAM and vivo Y11 2019 offer long battery life.


Latest Android Pie Mobile Phones List (Jul 2023): Phones like Elephone U3H, OPPO A12 and OPPO A12 64GB were launched in the last 30 days.
